Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.61,0:00:05.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:09.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because everyone is going to go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:13.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama, Papa, and my precious \Nlittle sister, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:17.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:22.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:25.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just happy that you remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:28.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:38.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing should be totally \Ndestroyed by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:44.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:47.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Half of those chains are still intact!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:48.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:51.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! This is taking too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:55.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But all we can do is cut \Nthrough them one at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:57.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, to the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:03.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:09.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more and my father's \Nwill can be carried out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:13.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Princess! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.70,0:01:15.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! At this rate, Lucy will...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:17.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:19.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna let you vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:22.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:02:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stand, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:01.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:02.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:06.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're a Man, you cry only \Nafter you do what needs to be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:07.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:09.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:12.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're cutting through \Nthe chains, so why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:14.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be in time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:16.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we're going to \Ndefeat the Six Generals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll back you up, Natsu-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:19.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:20.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Klodoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:25.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me. I'm not \Nlettin' anybody get in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys snap that stick in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna knock the sneer \Nright off this one's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:36.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy and Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:47.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Titania...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:51.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you finish me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:57.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you... Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:06.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your flames will never burn me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, your magic will run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:18.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you're totally on the defensive. \NI got you shakin' in your boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:24.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loathe me. But also fear and respect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I received my power by \Nmaking a huge sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:30.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm as powerful as my father now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Become a resident of the \NWorld of Nil, Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Genesis Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:43.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cast open the Gate of Wraithwail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Travelers of nothingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:53.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,devour that man's soul, his \Nmemories, his very existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease to exist, in the name of Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:00.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:00.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fitting for two friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:08.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're caught in a world of darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:12.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,while the little girl is trapped \Nin time without an exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:20.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's the best birthday present ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make this girl my little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Be friends with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:36.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I call her? \NI know! Maybe Gonzales?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:39.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think you should use a cuter name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had so much fun then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:45.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that big mansion... It was like a castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:51.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san, you made all kinds of clothes \Nfor me out of paper and flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:57.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We went everywhere together. And \Nwe smiled wherever we went...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:03.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:07.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...was always in front \Nof Mama's grave, crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:13.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I took it out on everyone and everything. I \Nthink I made everyone really worry about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:17.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I could do was watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard not being able to do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:25.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I looked at you, I was reminded \Nof Mama, and that became painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:30.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You stopped \Ntalking to me altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:37.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I left you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:42.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you waited all that time for \Nme to come back, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:54.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. She didn't mean to abandon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:58.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that she's so sad \Nnow after losing her mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:02.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,she can't bear to see you \Nor anything, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:07.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to talk \Nto my daughter these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:13.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...when she gets over her mother's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:22.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...will you become her little sister again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited for years after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:33.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The once lively mansion \Nwas now deathly quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, everyone was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:43.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the person who came \Nfor me wasn't you, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was given life, as Imitatia,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and did as I was told, pretending \Nto be Michelle Lobster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My mission was to retrieve \Nthe Infinity Clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before, you said you helped \Nmy father with his work...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:04.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:08.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was difficult using Uncle like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:10.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I wanted to go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:14.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to go back to those days...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:17.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:23.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a lot had happened \Nbetween you and Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:26.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Families are a mystery...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:35.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, their \Nfeelings always keep them connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's alive somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:46.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know she'll come back, so I want you \Nto find her and give that to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:48.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:49.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:56.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But magic is a mysterious and \Nmarvelous thing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:00.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:03.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you can become her little sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Michelle. It must've \Nbeen so hard on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:25.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to cry, Nee-san. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you can hear them, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The voices of the people who love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:34.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear them! I can see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:47.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:51.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster! We have to go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, on to the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened with the \Nrest of the Six Generals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren! What's the status \Nof Natsu and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, what's going on?! \NI've lost contact with Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:11.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The brat's existence was devoured \Nin the darkness and wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:15.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Lucy! I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:16.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:21.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good... I'm losing consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:26.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something... I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:31.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Struggle as he might, there's \Nno way he can get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:34.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Dragon Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... can go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:43.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You make Lucy and Michelle cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep crying forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:52.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to Michelle! Give Natsu back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:57.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's blinding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:05.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:10.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The R-system?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:14.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's... Real Nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! The girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With just one engraved seal left,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it must be impossible to have complete \Ncontrol over the Infinity Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:29.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:31.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:36.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lucy! She used the Infinity \NClock to sic Real Nightmare on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:40.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice, you say? My ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They say magic is in the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:47.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The more feelings you throw away, \Nthe more power you can attain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:52.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa! I literally \Nnever dreamed this could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:57.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To think the girl would be able to take \Nover the Infinity Castle?! So, toodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:11:58.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself a Man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:00.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:05.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you think you'll be able to meet someone \None day, you can't stop thinking about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more \Npainful than the sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:12.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,of cutting out that feeling, \Nthat possibility yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:18.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you sayin' you sacrificed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:28.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The future... A future in which \NI'm reunited with my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:31.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he saying that in exchange for power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:34.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,he made something that {\i1}could{\i0} happen into \Nsomething that's not going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:38.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a front-loading way of looking \Nbackwards. He must be sharp...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:41.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that? Now you lost me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna see your dad, \Ngo an' see him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:47.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You people caused a rift \Nbetween me and my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you haven't forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:54.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Repaying kindness with resentment? But \Nthat's no reason to make Lucy cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:56.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a roundabout way of doin' things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sacrificed the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:02.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talkin' big about things that \Nain't even happened yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:09.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:09.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we went over a lot of things and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:18.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we discovered something that we \Nhad to tell you about right away, actually!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?! Say that one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! He's overpowering me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:31.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand how you're \Nthinkin' about your dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:35.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't gain anything from the \Npower of feelings by tossin' them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's somethin' that's engraved in you \Nsomewhere and you gain from that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:43.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong! Because you throw them away, because \Nyou lose them, their importance shines!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:44.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:49.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're warped every which way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:53.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you look at things, the \Nway you feel, it's twisted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:58.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the past, the \Nfuture, even your own heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't face any of it head on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:04.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:09.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You say I'm not facing my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy did it to her father, \NMichelle did it to Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:15.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They tackled each other head on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:18.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got no right to laugh at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you lost to the power of feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:35.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He beat the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:48.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do? We were too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:55.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! We made all the \Nengraved seals get erased!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:59.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us Lucy back! Somebody answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:06.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do they mean I'm gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Don't tell me this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:12.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bad feeling about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:13.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:14.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-nee's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell Lucy all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not telepathy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:22.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:25.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Lucy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:28.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...totally merged with the Infinity Castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:32.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this huge fish castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:35.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is Lucy's body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:44.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too cruel... I've \Nbecome food for Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:45.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:47.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:52.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By using Real Nightmare to help Natsu, \Nyou only sped up the merging process!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, it's my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I finally got through!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, listen! A little while \Nago, I got a call from the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:05.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean-Luc and the others found \Nanother way to save Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean-Luc?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The "actually" guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:13.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the engraved seals aren't erased \Nin time, and merging occurs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:18.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then Lucy-sama must focus on remaining \Nconscious and controlling Real Nightmare, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:21.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We found out the one thing that can \Nstop the Infinity Clock in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:26.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is the magic siphoned from the \NCelestial Spirit Wizard bio-links!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:30.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to break the spells that \Nhave all of them in a chrysalis-like state.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:32.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple method.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:36.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will their sense of time \Nbe 100 years from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is, then the clock will \Nbreak up into its component parts
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and scatter somewhere again, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:43.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:51.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We know what to do from \Nthe merging to release...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:55.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if something goes wrong, all \Nthe parts will fly away somewhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:57.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't there any other way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:02.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:08.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, a lot of people will be able \Nto wake up from 100-year sleeps, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I may fly off somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:15.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only risk?! \NI'm a Fairy Tail wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the daughter of Jude and Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:23.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Michelle's big sister! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:36.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:38.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:41.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:42.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:01.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're terribly wounded... If \Nthere's anything I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you touch me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:08.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me... Are you the one that called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:11.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:16.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:24.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:26.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my sight so I could gain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:36.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Just from hearing voices, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:38.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:39.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:41.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erik...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:48.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cobra of the new Oracion Seis, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:52.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already taken your comrades into \Ncustody, so why don't you come quietly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:54.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Council, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:56.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! This man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:58.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:00.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:01.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl doesn't seem to be a wizard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:10.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. Anyone who conspires \Nwith the Six Generals has to be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:15.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:17.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:22.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! It was you, wasn't it?! You're \Nthe one who called out to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:24.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:27.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:31.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A comrade of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Never saw her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like she was just wandering \Naround here looking for her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:40.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:43.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving up awfully easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:44.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:46.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:49.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends are good things to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just knowing that you have \None has a calming effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:00.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erik... You called me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear my voice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:10.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally heard your voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:22.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:25.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where are we?! On top of an octopus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:31.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic! We're joined together with \NKanaloa-kun by the parfum of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. We're on the same side...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:36.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy... Where's Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:41.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren and the others are \Nlooking for her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:45.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I calm down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:52.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's scent! I'm sure of it! \NGo over that way, octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanaloa-kun, if you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:59.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, after all of my preparations, \Nit turned out like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have turned the \NSix Generals over to that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:08.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll just have to become Brain III \Nand assemble the next Six Generals...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! A clock hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away. We'll \Nsleep for eternity together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:16.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Stop it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:27.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:30.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the Infinity Castle and Oracion Seis...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:33.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...had vanished somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:39.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our journey began with the hand of a clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:42.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The events surrounding the \NKey of the Starry Heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...came to an end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, my room seemed empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.39,0:22:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like it suddenly became very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:10.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:15.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. So don't worry about me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:17.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:20.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:24.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for my beautiful little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:58.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I kicked Brain II's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.93,0:24:00.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone got a piece of the action, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.65,0:24:03.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail really is the \Nstrongest guild around!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.05,0:24:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest guild, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:08.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Natsu, during the seven \Nyears that we were on Tenroujima,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.55,0:24:11.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a guild called \NFiore's Strongest appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! Who the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.36,0:24:16.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.09,0:24:19.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's beat 'em and take our \N"strongest" title back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.69,0:24:22.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, all you ever think about are showdowns!
